{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840355341,"sessionID":"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1","part":{"id":"prt_d78554d7b001syoZ0fVbY7pgZY","messageID":"msg_d7854ac74001dJ51vpHuAZW6mY","sessionID":"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","offset":1,"limit":60},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube CRD Type Definitions\n2: \n3: This proposal defines the Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types for the AgentCube project.\n4: \n5: ---\n6: \n7: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: Define the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads. This work establishes the core API surface — `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and supporting shared types — that the Workload Manager controller and generated `client-go` library consume.\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: ### In scope\n16: \n17: | Item | Detail |\n18: |------|--------|\n19: | **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\n20: | **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n21: | **Version** | `v1alpha1` |\n22: | **Types defined** | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n23: | **Scheme registration** | `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go` — `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`, kind constants, `Resource()` helper |\n24: | **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn`, validation/default markers |\n25: | **Code generation** | `controller-gen crd` → `manifests/charts/base/crds/`; `controller-gen object` → `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`; `k8s.io/code-generator` → `client-go/` |\n26: | **Generated client surface** | `AgentRuntimeInterface` (Create/Update/UpdateStatus/Delete/DeleteCollection/Get/List/Watch/Patch), `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` |\n27: \n28: ### Out of scope\n29: \n30: - `CodeInterpreter` CRD types (separate AR)\n31: - Workload Manager HTTP API routes and handlers\n32: - Reconciler/controller logic\n33: - Helm chart CRD YAML rendering (consumes output, not produced here)\n34: - RBAC / ServiceAccount definitions\n35: \n36: ## Design\n37: \n38: ### File layout\n39: \n40: | File | Role |\n41: |------|------|\n42: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` | `+groupName` marker, `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme` |\n43: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Kind constants (`AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`), `SchemeGroupVersion`, `Resource()` helper |\n44: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus` |\n45: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\n46: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Auto-generated by `controller-gen object` |\n47: \n48: ### Type definitions\n49: \n50: **`AgentRuntime`** — namespaced CRD with `status` subresource:\n51: \n52: ```go\n53: // +genclient\n54: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n55: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n56: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n57: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n58: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n59: type AgentRuntime struct {\n60:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n\n(Showing lines 1-60 of 541. Use offset=61 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube CRD Type Definitions\n\nThis proposal defines the Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types for the AgentCube project.\n\n---\n\n# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads. This work establishes the core API surface — `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and supporting shared types — that the Workload Manager controller and generated `client-go` library consume.\n\n## Scope\n\n### In scope\n\n| Item | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\n| **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775840355328,"end":1775840355338}}}}
