{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840415468,"sessionID":"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1","part":{"id":"prt_d78563032001o4ZTQRg8v84JMk","messageID":"msg_d7856127e001TFVzl5igyOfUSd","sessionID":"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1","type":"text","text":"Done. I've updated `proposal.md` with the AR-002 section for **CodeInterpreter CRD Type Definition**.\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\nThe proposal now contains two main sections:\n\n### AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 (Existing)\nThe original AgentRuntime CRD proposal with all its details preserved.\n\n### AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 (New)\nAdded a comprehensive proposal section covering:\n\n- **Purpose**: Defines CodeInterpreter CRD for Kubernetes-native code execution environments\n- **Scope**: In-scope items (types, scheme registration, code generation) and out-of-scope items\n- **Design**: File layout, type definitions including:\n  - `CodeInterpreterPhase` enum (Pending/Running/Succeeded/Failed)\n  - `CodeInterpreter` root CRD with kubebuilder markers\n  - `CodeInterpreterSpec` (Image, Resources, Env, TimeoutSeconds, MaxMemoryMB)\n  - `CodeInterpreterStatus` (Phase, Conditions, SandboxID, ExecutionCount, etc.)\n  - `CodeInterpreterList`\n  - Scheme registration updates to `register.go`\n  - Code generation pipeline\n- **Impact Analysis**: Files created/modified/generated, downstream consumers, breaking change risk\n- **Alternatives Considered**:\n  1. Extend AgentRuntime vs separate CRD (rejected - distinct lifecycle semantics)\n  2. Use v1beta1 version (rejected - unnecessary complexity)\n  3. Embed full PodSpec (rejected - controlled API surface preferred)\n  4. Separate API group (rejected - shared runtime concerns)\n- **Dependencies**: Same as AR-001 (k8s.io/apimachinery, k8s.io/api, controller-runtime, etc.)\n- **Verification**: Build, test, and validation commands","time":{"start":1775840415466,"end":1775840415466}}}
